<div style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; font-family: sans-serif; color: #1f2937;">
  <h2 style="margin-bottom: 4px;">Your event was approved 🎉</h2>
  <p><strong><%= @event.title %></strong> is now live.</p>

  <p style="margin: 24px 0;">
    <a href="<%= @host_tools_url %>" style="background: #4f46e5; color: #fff; padding: 10px 18px; border-radius: 6px; text-decoration: none;">Open Host Tools</a>
  </p>
  <p style="font-size: 13px; color: #6b7280;">Host Tools lets you see RSVPs, mark attendance, and contact attendees — no login needed. Keep the link private.</p>

  <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #9ca3af;">Sent by <%= @event.organization.name %>.</p>
</div>
